
<div class="bingo-intro">
	<p>Ever sit on a conference call all day, twiddling your thumbs,
		wishing there was something better to do with your time? Well,
		here's a bingo game to help you keep track of the buzzwords of
		the day...</p>
</div>

<!-- Initial Button Options -->
<div class="row" id="bingo-btns">
	<div class="col-xs-12 btn-container">
		<button class="btn btn-primary" id="bingo-games-btn">Let me join or start a live game</button>
		<button class="btn btn-primary" id="bingo-single-btn">Show me a card - I'll play by myself</button>
		<button class="btn btn-primary" id="bingo-custom-btn">I want to generate a custom card</button>
	</div>
</div>

<!-- Back button (replaces initial options) -->
<div class="row" style="display: none;" id="bingo-back-container">
	<div class="btn-container">
		<button class="btn btn-primary" id="bingo-back-btn">Go Back</button>
	</div>
</div>

<!-- One-off card generation -->
<div id="bingoCardInput"style="display: none;">
	<div>
		<p>Use the form below to create a set of buzzwords from which to generate a bingo card.
		You must have at least 30 entries so that there's an element of randomness when generating
		the card!</p>
	</div>
	<div class="row">
		<div  class="col-sm-8">
			<div class="input-group">
				<input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Enter a buzzword or phrase..." id="addBuzzword" />
				<span class="input-group-btn">
					<input type="submit" class="btn btn-default" id="buzzwordSubmit" value="Add Buzzword" />
				</span>
			</div>

			<form>
				<select class="form-control" id="buzzwords" size="10" multiple></select><br>
				<button type="button" class="btn btn-default" id="removeBuzzwords">Remove Selected</button>
				<button type="button" class="btn btn-success pull-right" id="generateCardBtn" style="display: none;">Generate Card!</button>
			</form>
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-4">
			<div class="row generateBuzzwords">
				<div class="col-sm-12">
					<p>Stuck? Select a number of pre-generated buzzwords to add:</p>
				</div>
				<div class="col-sm-12">
					<div class="input-group">
						<select class="form-control"id="numAdditionalBuzzwords">
							{{#for 1 31 1}}
								<option>{{this}}</option>
							{{/for}}
						</select>
						<span class="input-group-btn">
							<input type="submit" class="btn btn-default" id="addBuzzwords" value="Add!" />
						</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div id="bingoCard" style="display: none;">
	{{#grouped_each 5 squares}}
	<div class="row">
		{{#each this}}
			<div class="square">
			    <div class="content">
						<img class="checkmark" src="/checkmark.png" />
						<div class="table">
							<div class="table-cell">
								<div>
										{{square_text}}
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
			    </div>
			</div>
		{{/each}}
	</div>
	{{/grouped_each}}
</div>
